where
description:
Where query filter
Accepts operators, see [Where operators](http://docs.spaceinvoices.com/?shell#where-operators) section for details.

name: and
description: Logical AND operator

name: or
description: Logical OR operator

name: include
description: Used to include related models

name: fields
description: Include or exclude certain fields

name: limit
description: Limit amount of data returned

name: order
description: Order results by property

name: skip
description: Number of results to skip

name: deleted
description: Also return deleted records. Only available on models that implement soft delete

name: src/services/paramBuilder.js
eq
description: Equivalence

name: neq
description: Not equal (!=)

name: gt
description:
Numerical greather than (>)
Valid for numberical and date values. For Geopoint values, the units are in miles by default.

name: gte
description:
Numerical greater than of equal (>=)
Valid for numberical and date values. For Geopoint values, the units are in miles by default.

name: lt
description:
Numerical less than (<)
Valid only for numerical and date values. For Geopoint values, the units are in miles by default.

name: lte
description:
Numerical less than or equal (<=)
Valid only for numerical and date values. For Geopoint values, the units are in miles by default.

name: between
description:
True if the value is between the two specified values
greater than or equal to first value and less than or equal to second value.

name: inq
description: In an array of values.

name: nin
description: Not in an array of values.

name: near
description:
For geolocations, return the closest points, sorted in order of distance.
Use with limit to return the n closest points.
maxDistance and unit can also be passed on same level as near to configure the search.

name: like
description: LIKE operators for use with regular expressions

name: nlike
description: NOT LIKE operators for use with regular expressions

name: regexp
description: Regular expression

name: _setValue
description: Sets the value to the filter builder

{
  "name": "spaceinvoices-api-client",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "",
  "main": "lib/spaceInvoices.js",
  "scripts": {
    "test": "mocha --require babel-register ./test/**/*.test.js",
    "lint": "standard-markdown && standard ./src/**/*.js ./test/**/*.js",
    "test:full": "yarn lint && yarn test",
    "coverage": "cross-env NODE_ENV=test nyc --reporter=text --reporter=text-summary mocha test/**/*.js",
    "coverage:travis": "cross-env NODE_ENV=test nyc --reporter=lcovonly mocha ./test/**/*.js && codecov",
    "docs": "esdoc",
    "runrun": "babel-node ./index.js",
    "clean": "rimraf lib/*",
    "precompile": "yarn run clean",
    "compile": "babel src --out-dir lib",
    "commit": "git add . && git-cz",
    "pregit": "yarn test && yarn compile && yarn docs",
    "gitit": "pregit && yarn commit"
  },
  "author": "Robert Tajnek",
  "license": "MIT",
  "dependencies": {
    "es6-error": "^4.1.1",
    "request": "^2.83.0",
    "request-promise": "^4.2.2",
    "urijs": "^1.19.1"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "babel-cli": "^6.26.0",
    "babel-core": "^6.26.0",
    "babel-plugin-istanbul": "^4.1.5",
    "babel-preset-env": "^1.6.1",
    "babel-register": "^6.26.0",
    "chai": "^4.1.2",
    "chai-as-promised": "^7.1.1",
    "codecov": "^3.0.0",
    "cross-env": "^5.1.3",
    "dotenv": "^5.0.1",
    "esdoc": "^1.0.4",
    "esdoc-standard-plugin": "^1.0.0",
    "eslint": "^4.18.2",
    "istanbul": "^0.4.5",
    "mocha": "^5.0.1",
    "nyc": "^11.4.1",
    "rimraf": "^2.6.2",
    "standard": "^11.0.0",
    "standard-markdown": "^4.0.2"
  },
  "config": {
    "commitizen": {
      "path": "cz-conventional-changelog"
    }
  },
  "standard": {
    "env": [
      "mocha"
    ],
    "ignore": [
      "lib"
    ]
  }
}
